{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Say goodbye to boring math drills! Use your math skills to defeat monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you take on the role of a hero and face off against monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Answer math problems to unleash powerful attacks and take down your enemies one by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With simple controls, you can improve your accuracy and speed while having fun! Embark on your adventure now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>[Choose Your Game Mode]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game offers two modes to suit your playstyle:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Training Mode: Practice as much as you want with no game over.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adventure Mode: Test your accuracy as mistakes lead to damage from monsters in this thrilling mode.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>[Customize Your Math Problems]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can freely mix and match problems from the following categories:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Addition (Levels 1, 2, 3)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Subtraction (Levels 1, 2, 3)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiplication</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Division</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose the math operations you want to practice!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432960/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738810276","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432960/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738810276","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432960/6ac5fbeb78b90518d1961450ff0644c0ad807f84/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738810276","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432960/6ac5fbeb78b9